{"tid":108762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該唔好再蝦南亞仔啦","createTime":"2017-02-05T13:25:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T11:45:31.000Z","uid":9564,"like":28,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e672bf958ab306977b1e0ec5564a1948cf0b92c","tid":108762,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:25:24.000Z","msg":"南亞人講真又無得罪過香港人<br />\n全亞洲有咁多人唔屌,做咩係要屌佢地既<br />\n個個人都應該要受尊重架嘛係咪先<br />\n係咪要全世界都覺得香港係歧視之都先<br />\n成日非我族類就反反反叫人返鄉下<br />\n佢地喺香港死慳死抵都係想做我地一份子啫<br />\n希望巴打們會清楚咁諗下呢幾日既攻擊行為<br />\n諗諗咁樣既行為光采唔光采,有無影衰埋香港人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4c889130481ff1a7c27f4bc6156e3a7f9999cc","tid":108762,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:26:24.000Z","msg":"南亞人全族死清光"},{"pid":"14731b24119673960148fc9bbd2de462768831af","tid":108762,"uid":78023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:27:04.000Z","msg":"算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0237cdd5404ab0909e9d19b6533f3ccf04cbabdd","tid":108762,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f42e7344148ea6867642ab1ce698164f96cef8","tid":108762,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:38:19.000Z","msg":"入嚟評個理"},{"pid":"170ba4fa30f13013af0336d62862eee6af4f4009","tid":108762,"uid":8733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:40:23.000Z","msg":"返哂鄉下咪冇得蝦"},{"pid":"47b1f2cc4f8eeb7f4c407b980c94c730c7191042","tid":108762,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dis